# Disclaimer for Investment / Trading Use

This repository contains code for backtesting, simulation, and educational
analysis of investment strategies. It is provided for educational and research
purposes only.

The authors do not provide investment advice or financial recommendations.
Past simulated performance does not guarantee future results. Users assume
all responsibility for any decisions made based on this code or its outputs.

This software does NOT execute real trades. All "trading" examples are
simulations using historical public market data.

This project is not affiliated with any registered investment advisor and
does not constitute "investment advisory business" under Japanese Financial
Instruments and Exchange Act (金融商品取引法).
